# **The Lion of Anacostia – Political Movements**

> _"Power concedes nothing without a demand. It never did and it never will."_ – Frederick Douglass

## 📌 Overview

**The Lion of Anacostia – Political Movements** is a pivotal **Africana Studies** topic, analyzing global leadership trends through the lens of Frederick Douglass and other Black leaders. This project examines the **strategies, rhetoric, and political mobilization** of historical and modern movements.

It supports **bias detection research in Africana Studies**, connecting with _The Lion of Anacostia_ to explore how Black political movements are framed in historical and contemporary narratives.

